	Lemfoerder are a leading OE supplier of rubber metal products and steering and suspension components for the majority of the European car market.</p>
<p>
	<a href="http://www.zf.com/brands/content/en/lemfoerder/homepage_lemfoerder/homepage_lemfoerder.jsp" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 11px; border: none; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(5, 106, 196); text-decoration: none; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Tahoma; " target="_blank">www.zf.com</a></p>
