	АЕ, Goetze and N&uuml;ral - these are the three brands of the company. They are leaders in engine parts products - pistons, valves, piston rings. They produce clutches, water , fuel and hydraulic pumps, suspension parts.</p>
<p>
	<a href="http://www.federalmogul.com/en/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 11px; border: none; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(5, 106, 196); text-decoration: none; font-family: Arial, Verdana, Tahoma; " target="_blank">www.federalmogul.com</a></p>
